[thinking] **Considering Java interfaces**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m diving into the issue of using a static Map in an interface. I think about serialization and how I need just the property value in the map, not as a field. A default setter can write to a static WeakHashMap, which feels a bit odd, but it seems to align with the pure JavaBean API. I'm also curious about how this interacts with native images. It’s worth testing with jshell to clarify things.
